{"type": "game", "name": "Pan-Pan", "steam_appid": 471920, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [508270, 508271], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fix your downed spaceship and find your way home. Explore a lush and colourful world littered with riddles and sprinkled with memorable characters. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About <strong>Pan-Pan</strong>:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pan-Pan is an adventure game with environmental narrative storytelling, exploration elements and puzzle solving. Enter a vibrant, colourful and quirky world where you unlock new areas by collecting items and solving riddles. Pan-Pan is created by SPELKRAFT in collaboration with Might &amp; Delight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Main features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set in an open world: Unlock new areas by collecting items and solving puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stellar soundtrack with soothing ambient sounds created by acclaimed sound producer Simon Viklund.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A balanced blend of exploration and puzzle solving game mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Story beats told through environmental interactions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use a mix of tools, gadgets and devices to solve puzzles and uncover the path home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fix your downed spaceship and find your way home. Explore a lush and colourful world littered with riddles and sprinkled with memorable characters. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About <strong>Pan-Pan</strong>:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pan-Pan is an adventure game with environmental narrative storytelling, exploration elements and puzzle solving. Enter a vibrant, colourful and quirky world where you unlock new areas by collecting items and solving riddles. Pan-Pan is created by SPELKRAFT in collaboration with Might &a